1. Videla sam veliku *baru* pored puta. (I saw a large *pond* next to the road.)
2. Ribolovci često idu na *bare* da love ribu. (Fishermen often go to *ponds* to fish.)
3. U ovom kraju ima mnogo *bara* koji se koriste za navodnjavanje. (There are many *reservoirs* in this area that are used for irrigation.)
4. *Bara* je stanište mnogih ptica i životinja. (A *marsh* is a habitat for many birds and animals.)
5. Potrebno je da popunite sve *bare* u formularu. (You need to fill in all the *blanks* in the form.)
6. Prošao je kroz *baru* i umalo se nije okliznuo. (He walked through a *puddle* and almost slipped.)
7. Bio je toliko umoran da je samo *barama* prelazio stranicu knjige. (He was so tired that he was just *skimming* the page of the book.)
8. Njihov odnos je postao toliko loš da više ne razgovaraju ni o čemu *bar* nekoliko meseci. (Their relationship became so bad that they haven't talked about *at least* anything for a few months.)
9. Većina ljudi voli *bare* pivo u letnjim mesecima. (Most people like *light* beer in the summer months.)
10. Njegov *bar* u centru grada je uvek pun posetilaca. (His *bar* in the city center is always crowded with visitors.)